Earth genasi, or Stone Princes as they call themselves, are Genasi descended from inhabitants of the Elemental Plane of Earth (Dao, pechs, Sandmen, and so on) or from deities of earth. They tend to be patient and contemplative. Possible traits include stonelike skin, eyes like black pits, eyes like gems, gravelly voices, very large hands and feat, iron gray hair, sweating mud instead of water, or a metallic sheen.
Sources: Planewalker's Handbook, Races of Faerun, Monsters of Faerun